description.en: Wincash coin is a cryptocurrency with SHA-256 algorithm, Pow, PoS, and Masternode. This coin is a cryptocurrency used as payment system in all Wincash projects. Wincash coin is established since august 2018 and has been used by thousand of people as a way of transaction in some of Wincash projects. Wincash coin uses PoW/PoS hybrid mechanism in the blockchain network to prevent 51% attack that commonly become a fatal issue in many new launched cryptocurrencies.
